dc_title_s: Nova orbis tabvla in lvcem edita, a F. de Wit.; Nova orbis tabula
dc_description_s: Includes ancillary maps of north and south polar regions. Scenes in 4 corners with images of the seasons, the elements and signs of the Zodiac. 1 map: hand col.; 2 hemispheres 27 cm. in diam., on sheet 54 x 63 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
